1.00.name: wordpress/user-level-themes
1.00.description:
The User Level Themes plugin allows a site administrator to select different themes for users with and without administrative access rights. This feature can be used to safely test a new theme while redirecting visitors to a known working theme. This plugin utilizes the [Wordpress Plugin Framework] (http://www.doubleblackdesign.com/categories/wordpress-plugins/wordpress-plugin-framework/ "Wordpress Plugin Framework") to provide a standard administration interface and allow for simplified plugin management.

License
